### RUNT - Consulta
POST http://localhost:8000/api/cotizaciones/runt
Authorization: Bearer {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "solicitud_aseguradora_id": "runt-001",
  "payload": {
    "in_strIDSolicitudCotizadora": "solicitud_123",
    "in_strPlaca": "ABC123",
    "in_strTipoDoc": "CC",
    "in_strNumDoc": "1234567890"
  }
}

###

### Batch - Múltiples aseguradoras
POST http://localhost:8000/api/cotizaciones/batch
Authorization: Bearer {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "aseguradora": "hdi",
    "solicitud_aseguradora_id": "batch-001",
    "payload": {
      "in_strPlaca": "ABC123",
      "in_strNumDoc": "1234567890"
    }
  },
  {
    "aseguradora": "sura",
    "solicitud_aseguradora_id": "batch-001",
    "payload": {
      "in_strPlaca": "ABC123",
      "in_strNumDoc": "1234567890"
    }
  }
]
